

Setting up nethack source for building static nethack library

Step1: Download and extract nethack-3.4.3 into this directory...

Step2: Setup sources for generating data and definitionfiles needed...
  cd nethack-3.4.3/sys/unix && chmod +x setup.sh
  ./setup.sh
  
Step3: 
  cd ../../util/ && make makedefs tileutils
  ./makedefs -odemvpqrhz
  ./tilemap

Step4: Make the data and build the nhdat file
  cd ../dat && make
  cd ../ && make dlb
  cp dat/nhdat ../../../../libs/armeabi/libnhdat.so

Step4: Build libnethackjni using android ndk